quran[6{c,v,t}:
6,132,har shakhs ka darja uss ke amal ke lehaaz se hai aur tumhara rab logon ke aamaal se be khabar nahi hai
6,133,tumhara rab be niaz hai aur meharbani is ka Shewa hai agar o hay chahay to tum logon ko le jaye aur tumhari jagah dosray jin logon ko chahay le aeye jis terhan uss ne tumhe kuch aur logon ki nasal se uthaya hai
6,134,tum se jis cheez ka wada kya ja raha hai woh yaqeenan anay wali hai aur tum khuda ko aajiz kar dainay ki taaqat nahi rakhtay
6,135,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! keh do ke logo! tum apni jagah amal karte raho aur mein bhi apni jagah amal kar raha hon, anqareeb tumhe maloom ho jaye ga ke injaam car kis ke haq mein behtar hota hai, bahar haal yeh haqeeqat hai ke zalim kabhi Falah nahi pa satke"
6,136,"inn logon ne Allah ke liye khud usi ki peda ki hui kheetion aur maweshion mein se aik hissa muqarrar kya hai aur kehte hain yeh Allah ke liye hai, bzam khud, aur yeh hamaray tehra-ay hue sharikon ke liye phir jo hissa un ke tehra-ay hue sharikon ke liye hai woh to Allah ko nahi pohanchana magar jo Allah ke liye hai woh un ke sharikon ko poanch jata hai kaisay buray faislay karte hain yeh log !"
6,137,"aur isi terhan bohat se mushrikon ke liye un ke sharikon ne apni aulaad ke qatal ko khushnuma bana diya hai taakay un ko halakat mein mubtala karen aur un par un ke deen ko mushtaba bana den agar Allah chahta to yeh aisa nah karte, lehaza inhen chore do ke apni aftara pardaaz yun mein lagey rahen"
